{"tid":2275431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄭若驊甩轆無極限　聆訊日期寫錯年份　陳志全：垃X圾","createTime":"2020-11-07T06:59:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-07T12:25:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":246,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"a8bdacaa3d183e1893c5b16a7787f219b208f730","tid":2275431,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T06:59:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/123978744_3558854754161026_1118188593480166773_o.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=jvHKSjGv1gAAX_zJUm5&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=9c0ecebf443327be52dcf91ae2343ecf&amp;oe=5FCD205F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F123978744_3558854754161026_1118188593480166773_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DjvHKSjGv1gAAX_zJUm5%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3D9c0ecebf443327be52dcf91ae2343ecf%26oe%3D5FCD205F&h=b8d4a2c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201107/photo/bkn-20201107103144994-1107_00822_001_02b.jpg?20201107142939\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201107%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201107103144994-1107_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20201107142939&h=c35014e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chanchichuen/photos/a.581965515183313/3558854750827693/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchanchichuen%2Fphotos%2Fa.581965515183313%2F3558854750827693%2F&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuMpe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=e10f2ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chanchichuen/photos/a.581965515183313/3558854750827693/</a><br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊又再「甩轆」！鄭若驊昨日(6日)去信法院提出介入議員陳志全私人檢控郭偉強普通襲擊一案，並稱將不提證供起訴。不過，有關信函卻寫錯年份，2020年寫錯成2019年，陳志全激動大鬧「律政司垃X圾」。<br />\n<br />\n外號「慢必」的陳志全在Facebook圖文並茂，指律政司將原定2020年11月9日的聆訊日期，寫錯成2019年11月9日，狠批「律政司垃X圾，聆訊日期都搞錯」。留言一出，網民就蜂擁評論，批評鄭若驊「幾十萬人工咁嘅水平，小學雞都不如」、「九流律政屍水平，攞一流人工」<br />\n<br />\n今年5月8日立法會內務委員會會議期間郭偉強拉扯陳志全衣領，令陳倒地受傷。陳提出私人檢控，獲法庭批准。<br />\n<br />\n案件原本排期下周一(9日)作審前覆核，但律政司去信西九龍裁判法院，申請介入案件，並稱會不提證供起訴，即被告不會被定罪。律政司提出下周一處理介入案件的申請，同時取消審前覆核。"},{"pid":"a7ecef148bd3164a4167451aff726504f9c3b07b","tid":2275431,"uid":196924,"like":236,"dislike":2,"score":234,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"咁咪即係佢封信無效，照告"},{"pid":"16ec137e5c6ff8e39cdd3ecd451ef61f65a46449","tid":2275431,"uid":237425,"like":114,"dislike":2,"score":112,"quote":{"pid":"a7ecef148bd3164a4167451aff726504f9c3b07b","tid":2275431,"uid":196924,"like":236,"dislike":2,"score":234,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"咁咪即係佢封信無效，照告"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:03:24.000Z","msg":"咪係，封信廢左啦"},{"pid":"4a88cb4f0d470770a92aae5083fbfee1f0b73d90","tid":2275431,"uid":203889,"like":225,"dislike":1,"score":224,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:04:46.000Z","msg":"嘩，真正draft呢封信果個人慘了<br />\n搞到上司出醜<br />\n應該會俾條老女人屌到爆"},{"pid":"acbcb92e05ae2b0c047cf860dcb17c9c2fd08e6b","tid":2275431,"uid":340088,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"咁樣撤銷呀？"},{"pid":"24f8bdb8e24a4e1e7ff740b1ea5381345325ae33","tid":2275431,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1da34862aafdb402dc07bbd26098d98ba7329d2","tid":2275431,"uid":97398,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"quote":{"pid":"16ec137e5c6ff8e39cdd3ecd451ef61f65a46449","tid":2275431,"uid":237425,"like":114,"dislike":2,"score":112,"quote":{"pid":"a7ecef148bd3164a4167451aff726504f9c3b07b","tid":2275431,"uid":196924,"like":236,"dislike":2,"score":234,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"咁咪即係佢封信無效，照告"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:03:24.000Z","msg